comment._content: Morane-Saulnier MoS 30 E1 (120 hp Le Rhone)

comment.author: 72347661@N02
comment._content:
This is a beauty. USAAS used 51 MoS 30 as fighter trainers at Issoudun.
Is anything more visible on the original photo at the top of the rudder, after MoS 32? That is the French serial number. Also very interesting to see that Morane-Saulnier already as early as this used the digit type number....
Stig
